{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"1831r–1","heading":"Notice of branch closure","label":"1831r–1 Notice of branch closure","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/ch16","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","CodificationSection was classified to prior to renumbering by .section 1831p of this titlePub. L. 102–550","Amendments1996—Subsec. (e). added subsec. (e).Pub. L. 104–2081994—Subsec. (d). added subsec. (d).Pub. L. 103–328"],"amendments":["Amendments1996—Subsec. (e). added subsec. (e).Pub. L. 104–2081994—Subsec. (d). added subsec. (d).Pub. L. 103–328"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Notice to appropriate Federal banking agency","label":"a Notice to appropriate Federal banking agency","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"An insured depository institution which proposes to close any branch shall submit a notice of the proposed closing to the appropriate Federal banking agency not later than the first day of the 90-day period ending on the date proposed for the closing.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Contents of notice","label":"2 Contents of notice","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/a/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fa%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a detailed statement of the reasons for the decision to close the branch; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/a/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fa%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"statistical or other information in support of such reasons.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Notice to customers","label":"b Notice to customers","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"An insured depository institution which proposes to close a branch shall provide notice of the proposed closing to its customers.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Contents of notice","label":"2 Contents of notice","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/b/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fb%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"posting of a notice in a conspicuous manner on the premises of the branch proposed to be closed during not less than the 30-day period ending on the date proposed for that closing; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/b/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fb%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/b/2/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/b/2/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fb%2F2%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"at least one of any regular account statements mailed to customers of the branch proposed to be closed, or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/b/2/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/b/2/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fb%2F2%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"in a separate mailing,","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Adoption of policies","label":"c Adoption of policies","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Each insured depository institution shall adopt policies for closings of branches of the institution.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Branch closures in interstate banking or branching operations","label":"d Branch closures in interstate banking or branching operations","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Notice requirements","label":"1 Notice requirements","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fd%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"In the case of an interstate bank which proposes to close any branch in a low- or moderate-income area, the notice required under subsection (b)(2) shall contain the mailing address of the appropriate Federal banking agency and a statement that comments on the proposed closing of such branch may be mailed to such agency.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Action required by appropriate Federal banking agency","label":"2 Action required by appropriate Federal banking agency","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fd%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fd%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/2/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/2/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fd%2F2%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"submits a written request relating to the closing of such branch to the appropriate Federal banking agency; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/2/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/2/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fd%2F2%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"includes a statement of specific reasons for the request, including a discussion of the adverse effect of such closing on the availability of banking services in the area affected by the closing of the branch; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fd%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the agency concludes that the request is not frivolous,","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":"No effect on closing","label":"3 No effect on closing","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fd%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"No action by the appropriate Federal banking agency under paragraph (2) shall affect the authority of an interstate bank to close a branch (including the timing of such closing) if the requirements of subsections (a) and (b) have been met by such bank with respect to the branch being closed.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":"Definitions","label":"4 Definitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fd%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":"Interstate bank defined","label":"A Interstate bank defined","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/4/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fd%2F4%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The term “interstate bank” means a bank which maintains branches in more than 1 State.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":"Low- or moderate-income area","label":"B Low- or moderate-income area","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/4/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fd%2F4%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/4/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/4/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fd%2F4%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"less than 80 percent of the median family income for the metropolitan statistical area (as designated by the Director of the Office of Management and Budget) in which the census tract is located; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/4/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/d/4/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fd%2F4%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"in the case of a census tract which is not located in a metropolitan statistical area, less than 80 percent of the median family income for the State in which the census tract is located, as determined without taking into account family income in metropolitan statistical areas in such State.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"e","heading":"Scope of application","label":"e Scope of application","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fe","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fe%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"an automated teller machine;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fe%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fe%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"occurs within the immediate neighborhood; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fe%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"does not substantially affect the nature of the business or customers served; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fe%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e/3/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fe%2F3%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e/3/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e/3/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fe%2F3%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"; orsection 1821(n) of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e/3/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e/3/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fe%2F3%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"subsection (f) or (k) of ; orsection 1823 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e/3/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t12/s1831r–1/e/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft12%2Fs1831r%E2%80%931%2Fe%2F3%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"any assistance provided by the Corporation under .section 1823(c) of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}]}
